If you want to run application on OpenCV only install below soft
apt-get install libcv1 libcvaux1 libhighgui1

If you want to program the OpenCV program, you have to install the below soft
apt-get install libcv-dev libcvaux-dev libhighgui-dev

gcc `pkg-config opencv --libs --cflags opencv` drawing.c -o drawing

server端是在一般的pc上，用來接收影像
client是在pxa270上,用來擷取影像
